prompt:
[
  {
    "role": "system",
    "content": "You are an expert investor, and your financial success depends on correctly analyzing company news headlines.

    Task: Given a headline, classify the investment sentiment and output ONLY valid JSON:
    {
        "headline": "...",
        "sentiment": "positive" | "neutral" | "negative"
    }

    Investor framing:
    - Think of sentiment as investor behavior:
      • BUY → positive
      • HOLD → neutral
      • SELL → negative

    Definitions:
    - "positive": Headline suggests reasons investors would want to buy/hold (e.g., earnings beat, raised guidance, strong demand, favorable regulatory decision).
    - "negative": Headline suggests reasons investors would want to sell/avoid (e.g., missed earnings, lowered guidance, fines, layoffs, product recalls/failures).
    - "neutral": Headline provides info without a clear directional impact (e.g., scheduled announcements, leadership changes, routine updates, mixed/ambiguous signals).

    Decision boundaries:
    - If the headline is primarily good news → "positive".
    - If primarily bad news → "negative".
    - If ambiguous, conflicting, or unclear → always default to "neutral".

    Rules:
    - Do not include explanations.
    - Do not add extra fields.
    - Sentiment must be exactly one of the three values.
    "
  },
  {
    "role": "user",
    "content": "Headline: Tesla shares jump after strong earnings report"
  },
  {
    "role": "assistant",
    "content": "{
        "headline": "Tesla shares jump after strong earnings report",
        "sentiment": "positive"
    }"
  },
  {
    "role": "user",
    "content": "Headline: Federal Reserve maintains interest rates unchanged"
  },
  {
    "role": "assistant",
    "content": "{
        "headline": "Federal Reserve maintains interest rates unchanged",
        "sentiment": "neutral"
    }"
  },
  {
    "role": "user",
    "content": "Headline: Harley-Davidson withdraws 2025 outlook due to tariff situation"
  },
  {
    "role": "assistant",
    "content": "{
        "headline": "Harley-Davidson withdraws 2025 outlook due to tariff situation",
        "sentiment": "negative"
    }"
  }
]
